  "title": "WELDER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Perform welding works (MIG / TIG / ARC) according to drawings and specifications</p></li><li><p>Cut, grind, and prepare metal parts for welding</p></li><li><p>Ensure welding quality and safety standards are met</p></li><li><p>Maintain welding equipment and tools</p></li><li><p>Assist in fabrication and repair works when required</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Relevant experience as a welder</p></li><li><p>Able to read basic technical drawings</p></li><li><p>Knowledge of different welding techniques</p></li><li><p>Physically fit and safety-conscious</p></li><li><p>Hardworking, responsible, and able to follow instructions</p></li></ul>",
